info.name: fiftyone-location
info.summary: The 51Degrees Pipeline API is a generic web request intelligence and data processing solution with the ability to add a range of 51Degrees and/or custom plug ins (Engines). This repository contains the geo-location engines for the Python implementation of the Pipeline API.
